Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New York bomb threats
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wb1k
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 May 1981
Police clear buildings as more than 260 bomb threats disrupt NY life. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.